s include enhancing LLM-generated narratives, aiding second-language writers in stylistic expression, and informing cognitive science models of metaphor comprehension. By formalizing stylistic coherence as a learnable, measurable objective, this work opens new directions in controllable text generation beyond factual accuracy toward aesthetic intelligence.",
